Text:
OBAMA: Lets turn America into a third world Kenya!

FOLLOWERS: Yeaaaaaah!

It boggles the mind how many Americans got caught by this soundbite.

For those still in blissful ignorance:
"You didn't build that" referred to stuff built by the government: roads, schools, the invention of the internet, etc. It did NOT refer to businesses. 

It is very clear, once you hear what Obama said right before the quoted fragment. He didn't formulate his thought in the clearest way and people are making a use of that. Fox News and other propaganda outlets leave that out on purpose and feed disinformation to its retarded lemming audience.

(I mean, how stupid one needs to be to watch Fox News or NBC.)
